{"tid":409724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「千年難得一見美少女」首度露出額頭　橋本環奈害羞了","createTime":"2017-09-22T09:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T05:17:58.000Z","uid":9573,"like":109,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90d35dbaa55e4f2618a57151f7878767a94796c1","tid":409724,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"日本女星橋本環奈因一張「奇蹟美照」打開知名度，被封為「千年難得一見美少女」，爆紅之後戲約、代言接不完，成為炙手可熱的新生代明星。造型百變的她，過去總是以短瀏海亮相，近來卻罕見露出額頭，實用面積1974方呎，成交價9870萬元新造型連自己也有些不習慣，「感覺很不好意思呢哈哈。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21616482_839984899515639_1582114422755260277_n.jpg?oh=4f00135b00bd5480b1f02a5d544c3be3&amp;oe=5A4E1B17\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21616482_839984899515639_1582114422755260277_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4f00135b00bd5480b1f02a5d544c3be3%26oe%3D5A4E1B17&h=04c66049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲當年14歲的橋本環奈因這張照片一夕爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈20日凌晨在推特上發文，曬出一系列美照，分享出為了雜誌拍攝，所準備的全新造型，「我從來沒露過額頭，感覺很不好意思呢哈哈。」畫面中，只見她穿著粉紅色平口洋裝，展露整片白皙香肩，並且以髮帶將瀏海往上翻，難得露出額頭造型驚豔眾人，呈現出可愛又略顯成熟的氣質美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2811/d2811879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2811%2Fd2811879.jpg&h=7a642ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2811/d2811880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2811%2Fd2811880.jpg&h=ba92fa3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2811/d2811881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2811%2Fd2811881.jpg&h=7638faa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈首度露出額頭。<br />\n<br />\n一系列照片曝光後，橋本環奈新造型獲得不少網友好評，引來大票粉絲留言狂讚，「好難得露額頭」、「千雪降臨啦」、「頭髮好可愛阿」、「新造型好好看」、「千年一遇美少女果然厲害」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573735.jpg&h=9c3af12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼橋本環奈先前直播公開剪短髮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573734.jpg&h=5090f1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橋本環奈最初以一張「奇蹟美照」打開知名度，原是「Rev.from DVL」的成員，團體解散後各自發展，她近來則是因演出電影《銀魂》和日劇《警視廳生物課》人氣再飆。前陣子，她開直播宣傳新戲的同時，也同步分享剪頭髮的過程，難得將多年長髮剪短，「這是我人生中最短的一次。」當時全新髮型同樣讓粉絲興奮不已，「整個人都變了」、「還是好可愛啊！」"},{"pid":"0eb24c6850f545e46681e321fede284e9cec6f53","tid":409724,"uid":37005,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"橋本真係好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1c8dde599606603c38092f9d37eabef55b0c3d","tid":409724,"uid":5499,"like":240,"dislike":1,"score":239,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322d1b2494a969295eb1fe8efe507965e2fb2703","tid":409724,"uid":62822,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48abbf65531634233f9a0bc4ab38a68297f3a9f9","tid":409724,"uid":37978,"like":222,"dislike":1,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"罕見露出額頭，實用面積1974方呎，成交價9870萬元新造型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a98fca46ad7ecb15c0379c4c06800521b6dbb76","tid":409724,"uid":28151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"<block